    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000530_00000",
      "en_US": [
        "That Badge...\n",
        "It’s from Sunyshore’s Gym?\r",
        "You’ve been to that port town, then...\r",
        "Would... Would you lend an ear to this\n",
        "old man’s tale?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000530_00001",
      "en_US": [
        "No...\n",
        "I shouldn’t burden you with this.\r",
        "My grandson grew up in that city by\n",
        "the sea.\r",
        "Worn down by trying to live up to his\n",
        "parents’ expectations, he found refuge\f",
        "in tinkering with machines.\r",
        "I wonder even now if I should have\n",
        "taken him in and raised him myself.\r",
        "Though I’m not certain if that would\n",
        "have been a good choice or not...\r",
        "I don’t think anyone could say.\r",
        "I’m sorry, I shouldn’t have said any\n",
        "of this to you..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000530_00002",
      "en_US": [
        "Ah...\n",
        "Pay me no heed, then.\r",
        "I only hoped to unburden myself of\n",
        "some guilt..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000530_00003",
      "en_US": [
        "There are many old and difficult-looking\n",
        "books here.\r",
        "“Space and the Galaxies”\n",
        "“The Beginning of Space”..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "pl_msg_00000530_00004",
      "en_US": [
